data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming Sleepy Hollow neighborhood of Amarillo, Texas! This delightful property is surrounded by majestic trees, creating a serene and tranquil atmosphere. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a bonus room, and a basement, this home offers both comfort and versatility. The kitchen is a culinary haven with 2 new double ovens, new microwave, and a new dishwasher. Plus a brand new hot water heater and new garage door just installed. The newer HVAC unit and class 4 roof provide peace of mind and energy efficiency. Enjoy the perfect balance of tranquility and convenience in Sleepy Hollow, where nature and vibrant amenities are just a short drive away.
